<section class="bg-white py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">HELOC vs. Cash-Out vs. Personal Loan</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
        Choose the right way to access your equity by comparing flexibility, payment structures, and costs.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-800">HELOC</h3>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-wallet text-4xl text-[#5c3f14] my-4" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-left text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong>Best for:</strong> Short-term projects, flexible access.</li>
          <li class="flex"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong>Payment Type:</strong> Pay interest only on the amount you draw.</li>
          <li class="flex"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong>Key Feature:</strong> Revolving credit line for repeated use.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-800">Cash-Out Refinance</h3>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-house-chimney-crack text-4xl text-gray-500 my-4" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-left text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong>Best for:</strong> Large, one-time projects or rate/term improvements.</li>
          <li class="flex"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong>Structure:</strong> Replaces your mortgage with a new fixed-rate loan.</li>
          <li class="flex"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong>Payment Type:</strong> Full principal and interest on entire new balance.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-800">Personal Loan</h3>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-file-invoice-dollar text-4xl text-gray-500 my-4" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-left text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong>Best for:</strong> Smaller loan amounts, no home equity needed.</li>
          <li class="flex"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong>Structure:</strong> Unsecured installment loan.</li>
          <li class="flex"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"></i><strong>Payment Type:</strong> Typically higher, fixed monthly payments.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

